snippet.title: Company of Heroes 3 // Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
#Companyofheroes is back! Next-gen action, award winning tactical gameplay and deeper strategy than ever. Tune in for the latest #CoH3 updates, such as modes, features, campaigns and more directly from the developers at Relic Entertainment. 

Add CoH3 to your wish list here ►
https://www.companyofheroes.com/en /

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Stay up to date on everything CoH3 in our official Discord ► https://discord.gg/companyofheroes
Share your feedback on our forums ► https://community.companyofheroes.com/

And Follow us on our socials here:
Twitter ►          https://twitter.com/CompanyOfHeroes
Instagram ►    https://www.instagram.com/companyofheroes/
